title: The Seventh Year
itunes:title: The Seventh Year
description:
The “seventh year” is when you break free from limitations that have held you back — debt, lack, sickness, insecurity, addictions, depression, constant struggle (Deuteronomy 15).You will take a deeper look at this seventh year and what it means for today. ----Visit https://joelosteen.com to receive daily updates and encouragement from Joel Osteen.----Have you followed Joel Osteen on Instagram? https://instagram.com/joelosteen.
